{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2ff6ba1bd","title":"谢富治在北京市革委会常委会议上谈河南问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d5d758ba1d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":5,"articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e11a0860cd","type":"title","text":"谢富治在北京市革委会常委会议上谈河南问题","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"},{"id":"d715fa4069","type":"paragraph","text":"五月五日晚，北京市革命委员会常委开会。北航红旗负责人韩爱晶同志问谢富治副总理：“河南问题怎么样了？”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"},{"id":"b0c2eceb97","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：“你们红代会支持的二七公社是对的。军区的作法是错误的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"},{"id":"dd2c6baf01","type":"paragraph","text":"韩：“为什么还不解决？”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"},{"id":"703fb5a317","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：不那么容易，中央文革现在把注意力都集中到外省了。中央正在着手解决河南问题。它牵涉到军区问题，不能一下解决，何运洪是错误的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd"}],"page":{"id":"437e25a82f","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2ff6ba1bd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}